// ch01 §1.1/ch08 Q13: checking is unconditional by default -- there is no
// more "native function" that's exempt. `main` here has no annotation at
// all (there is no annotation to give), and INT_MAX + 1 must still abort,
// exactly as it would inside any other function.
int main() {
    int x = 2147483647;
    return x + 1;
}
